{"tid":2078475,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"列七條件施壓 揚言解封熱兵器  印火爆司令下通牒「隨時對華開戰」","createTime":"2020-06-25T05:25:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-25T07:43:55.000Z","uid":25558,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"cb282293a00f3d6d45434ad527c86ba5163fe43b","tid":2078475,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T05:25:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200625/JFCLFFWRHZUKFEKKXL6OJC4GWU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200625%2FJFCLFFWRHZUKFEKKXL6OJC4GWU%2F&d=tWDRN%2F4Vza2V0D3%2FQI2QfQRUsGYs0X8VP9vM6mjQjJM%3D&h=90bf4bdb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200625%2FJFCLFFWRHZUKFEKKXL6OJC4GWU%2F&h=0f305d1e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200625/JFCLFFWRHZUKFEKKXL6OJC4GWU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n列七條件施壓 揚言解封熱兵器 <br />\n印火爆司令下通牒「隨時對華開戰」<br />\n<br />\n【中印衝突】<br />\n<br />\n本月15日中印邊境衝突事件未了，雙方22日恢復軍長級談判，雖兩國都宣稱談判達成共識，兩軍脫離接觸，但印媒透露，印方談判主官、第14集團軍軍長辛格（Harinder Singh）提出七大條件，包括中方從爭議地區撤軍、停止增兵邊境等，儼如「最後通牒」。辛格又稱印軍已做好對中方「全面戰爭準備」。中國國防部昨回應指，此次事件是印方挑起造成，責任完全在印方。中方軍媒斥印方自以為是，對中方死亡人數「惡意造謠」。<br />\n<br />\n包括《印度斯坦時報》（Hindustan Times）、《金融快報》（Financial Express）等印媒昨報道，印度第14集團軍長辛格中將與中國西部戰區轄下南疆軍區司令柳林少將22日在中印實際控制線中國一側的摩爾多（Moldo）邊境檢查站舉行會議，經11個小時對話後達成共識：雙方把部隊從衝突地帶撤離，同時雙方部署在各自實際控制線附近的坦克和戰機，也一併撤離。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/sWK7MTv3PSGIglAgGjM7ftQ860c=/190x158/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JEBOGI72VGRS4B6FBC24D2F7IU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FsWK7MTv3PSGIglAgGjM7ftQ860c%3D%2F190x158%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJEBOGI72VGRS4B6FBC24D2F7IU.jpg&h=aff7e40f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n印度軍頭辛格（中）以火爆見稱，對華態度強硬。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n兩國宣稱已達撤軍共識<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：爆小型槍戰「可能性很大」<br />\n<br />\n印媒透露，辛。。。。。。。。。。。。，並已授權前線指揮官與中方打交道時「完全自由」的指令。<br />\n<br />\n報道未提及中方態度如何，。。。。。。。。。。。。。單方挑釁造成」。<br />\n<br />\n吳謙同時透露，西。。。。。。。。。。。。。。，內地網上充斥對印度開戰的呼聲。<br />\n<br />\n印度第14集團軍是一支專門針對中國。。。。。。。。。。。。，在印軍內部以驕橫聞名。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ctVDf0zkGxZZ65CYhvNXkO9lGWE=/190x293/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MADHOEMLWUUXIARPKMKUE7EFG4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FctVDf0zkGxZZ65CYhvNXkO9lGWE%3D%2F190x293%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMADHOEMLWUUXIARPKMKUE7EFG4.gif&h=5e1df1b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n印煞停46億元貿協<br />\n<br />\n印度當局還煞停與中國簽。。。。。。。。。。。。國船貨進行額外檢查，報復中方。<br />\n<br />\n路透社/環球網"},{"pid":"8ddf2c2e889d4a160b2b14713102648a06c7aa58","tid":2078475,"uid":39010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T05:27:05.000Z","msg":"唔會ge  <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6454e06eb5c0b4892118f638dc59e96acabbfd7","tid":2078475,"uid":41545,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T05:28:55.000Z","msg":"邊會打 印度仔有種滅天朝大軍比我地見識下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d21a121bb61b2279dd54c02d9ccf83f77afa3e9d","tid":2078475,"uid":253016,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T05:29:31.000Z","msg":"印度佬唔好得個UP字"},{"pid":"e583755ee40f8238a34682cdd863f47f54a0b319","tid":2078475,"uid":251732,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T05:30:58.000Z","msg":"唔好意思可唔可以借個位？<br />\n<br />\n所有人唔可以再等落去 《香港最後呼喚宣告書》<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2078074\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2078074</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6fd55ed38ce44790ca7586f8c8290ee143460310","tid":2078475,"uid":58841,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"202